ZH: 你干吗不理我？
EN: Why are you ignoring me?

ZH: 他们在干吗呢？
EN: What are they doing?

ZH: 你干吗这么晚才回家？
EN: Why did you come home so late?

ZH: 干吗把这件事藏得这么深？
EN: Why hide this matter so deeply?

ZH: 你干吗要跟我说谎？
EN: Why do you need to lie to me?

ZH: 干吗要这么卖力工作？
EN: Why do you need to work so hard?

ZH: 他们干吗一起笑呢？
EN: Why are they laughing together?

ZH: 干吗要戴着墨镜进屋？
EN: Why wear sunglasses while entering the house?

ZH: 你干吗那么着急？
EN: Why are you in such a rush?

ZH: 你干吗看着我发呆？
EN: Why are you staring at me blankly?

ZH: 干吗非得争吵不可？
EN: Why do we have to argue?

ZH: 你干吗不跟我交流？
EN: Why don't you communicate with me?

ZH: 他干吗不吃饭就睡觉？
EN: Why does he sleep without eating?

ZH: 干吗不跟家人一起过节？
EN: Why not celebrate with family?

ZH: 你干吗不让我帮助你？
EN: Why won't you let me help you?

ZH: 为什么干吗要这样子对待他？
EN: Why treat him like this?

ZH: 干吗不跟我商量一下？
EN: Why not discuss with me?

ZH: 你干吗要跟我道歉？
EN: Why do you need to apologize to me?

ZH: 干吗不做点什么？
EN: Why not do something?

ZH: 他干吗不说实话？
EN: Why doesn't he tell the truth?
